messages.aimFire1:
Mira e spara al contenitore di fronte.
Mouse: move and {controlStrings/mouse/fire}
Keyboard: {controlStrings/keyboard/yawLeft}, {controlStrings/keyboard/yawRight}, {controlStrings/keyboard/pitchUp}, {controlStrings/keyboard/pitchDown} and {controlStrings/keyboard/fire}
Joystick: move the stick and {controlStrings/joystick/fire}

messages.aimFire2:
Distruggi il contenitore. Continua a colpirlo finché non esplode.
Mouse: move and {controlStrings/mouse/fire}
Keyboard: {controlStrings/keyboard/yawLeft}, {controlStrings/keyboard/yawRight}, {controlStrings/keyboard/pitchUp}, {controlStrings/keyboard/pitchDown} and {controlStrings/keyboard/fire}
Joystick: move the stick and {controlStrings/joystick/fire}
